        "body": "The best stuff savings buy isn't stuff:\n- **Less stress** — surprises lose their fangs\n- **Confidence** — you've got your own back\n- **Independence** — no begging, no IOUs\n\nEven $100 saved feels completely different from $0.\n\nOne trick makes the habit survive weak moments: keep savings in a separate account from spending money. Out of sight, out of cart."
