        "body": "Spend $10 on a game skin and it's gone forever. Invest that $10 and it has a shot at becoming $15, $20, or more — because investing means using money today to grow more money tomorrow.\n\nThink of it like planting a tree. You bury a seed (your cash), water it (add a little regularly), and wait. Years later it's dropping fruit — money your money made — while you do absolutely nothing.",
